\fs20 \cf0 Correctly use the HTML's built-in semantic structure to create natural document hierarchy and meaningful structure. Headings are particularly important.
\fs24 \
\
\pard\intbl\itap1\pardeftab709

\b\fs20 \cf0 Natural linear order
\b0\fs24 \
\pard\intbl\itap1\pardeftab709

\fs20 \cf0 Natural, logical reading ordering is a good place to start. A screen reader reads  in the order of the defined natural language. Use CSS to layout things out visually and to create meaningful blocks to visual users.
\fs24 \
\
\pard\intbl\itap1\pardeftab709

